				Implementation detail
				<pre>
when a click happened 
count 0,1

count 0: black
count 1: white

already placed: no response 
empty: 
i. valid 
a. place white/black
b. apply flip
c. determine if game over
ii. invalid
no response

class 
Board
init:
-1: empty

0: black
1: white

count: whose turn

isValid() // according to count and board status
{
check all the existing same color pieces
a. distance &gt; 1 (|x| + |y|)
b. same row/column, diagonal 
c. all other color pieces between
1. distance, same row/column or diagonal. 
2. all between pieces are white --&gt; return true; ow continue

}
</pre>
			</li>
			<li>
				Points of attention
				<ul>
					<li>
						between: not inclusive</li>
					<li>
						diagonal: distance should be greater than 2</li>
					<li>
						revert piece should happen for every valid pair</li>
				</ul>
			</li>
